<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681203>
    dc:description "FIGURE 19. Bebaiotes macroptera sp. nov. holotype male: A. Male habitus, lateral view; B. Female, habitus, lateral view; C. Male head, anterior view; D. Male head and thorax, dorsal view; E. Male abdominal process, lateral view; F. Female, abdomen, lateral view. Scale bars: A, B= 1 mm; C, D = 0.3 mm; E = 0.4 mm; F = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681203/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681205>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Bebaiotes macroptera sp. nov., male genitalia: A. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; B. Pygofer, lateral view; C. Anal tube, dorsal view; D. Gonostyli, right lateral view; E. Gonostyli, dorsal view; F. Periandrium and inner sclerotised plates, lateral view; G. Periandrium and inner sclerotised plates, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–G = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681205/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681207>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Bebaiotes macroptera sp. nov., female: A. Anal tube, dorsal view; B. Pygofer posterior view; C. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; D. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula), dorsal view; E. Gonapophysis VIII (first valvula), lateral view. Scale bars: A–E = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681207/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681245>
    dc:description "FIGURE 38. Antennae of Bebaiotes species. A. Bebaiotes macroptera sp. nov.; B. Bebaiotes parallela sp. nov.; C. Bebaiotes pennyi sp. nov.; D. Bebaiotes pulla Muir, 1934; E. Bebaiotes tigrina sp. nov.; F. Bebaiotes wilsoni sp. nov. Scale bars: A–F = 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681245/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681249>
    dc:description "FIGURE 40. Wings of Bebaiotes species. A. Bebaiotes dorsivittata Fennah, 1947, forewing; B. Bebaiotes dorsivittata Fennah, 1947, hind wing; C. Bebaiotes guianesus (Fennah, 1947), forewing; D. Bebaiotes guianesus (Fennah, 1947), hind wing; E. Bebaiotes macroptera sp. nov., forewing; F. Bebaiotes macroptera sp. nov., hind wing; G. Bebaiotes parallela sp. nov., forewing; H. Bebaiotes parallela sp. nov., hind wing. Scale bars: A–H = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681249/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681253>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Geographical distribution of Bebaiotes species. Bebaiotes amazonica sp. nov.; Bebaiotes bia sp. nov.; Bebaiotes dichromata sp. nov.; Bebaiotes macroptera sp. nov." ;
